[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_0",
    "text": "2.人口东多西少",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10785681078568107,
      0.15942028985507245,
      0.2547652254765225,
      0.17984189723320157
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_1",
    "text": "(1)人口完度：我国平均人口密度为每平方干米134人，是世界平均人口密度的3倍 (2)人口分布特点：以黑河(黑龙江省)——腾冲(云南省)为界，东多西少。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13389121338912133,
      0.18840579710144928,
      0.8777312877731288,
      0.2437417654808959
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_2",
    "text": "(3)34个省级行政区中.人口最多的是河南省.人口最少的是澳门特别行政区.人口 密度最大的是澳门特别行政区，人口密度最小的是西藏自治区。23个省中，人口密度最 大的是江苏省.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09483960948396095,
      0.2523056653491436,
      0.9279404927940493,
      0.33662714097496704
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_3",
    "text": "多民族的大家庭",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.09669920966992096,
      0.37681159420289856,
      0.27615062761506276,
      0.39855072463768115
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_4",
    "text": "1、56个民族",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10320781032078104,
      0.4090909090909091,
      0.22501162250116225,
      0.4288537549407115
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_5",
    "text": "(0人□数最多的是汉族，占全国人□总数的92%.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1292422129242213,
      0.4400527009222661,
      0.596931659693166,
      0.4624505928853755
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_6",
    "text": "(②)少数民族人口最多的是壮族，最少是珞巴族，人口在400万以上的少数民族有 壮族。满族、回族、苗族、维吾尔族、彝族、土家族、蒙古族、藏族。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09112040911204092,
      0.47035573122529645,
      0.9270106927010693,
      0.5250329380764164
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_7",
    "text": "(3)各民族有独特的风俗习惯，文化艺术和传统的体育活动.如汉族的端干节. 傣族的泼水节.蒙古族的那达慕大会、维吾不族的开斋节.彝族的火把节、朝鲜族 的长鼓舞等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09205020920502092,
      0.5316205533596838,
      0.9307298930729893,
      0.6179183135704874
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_8",
    "text": "(4) 民族政策：各民族不论大小、一律平等.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1301720130172013,
      0.6271409749670619,
      0.5346350534635054,
      0.6508563899868248
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_9",
    "text": "2.民族的分布",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09298000929800093,
      0.6903820816864296,
      0.25383542538354253,
      0.7114624505928854
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59_10",
    "text": "(1)民族分布持点：大杂居.小聚居. (2)汉族：遍及全国.主要集中在东部和中部 (3)少数民族：主要分布在西南.西北和东北部地区",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12738261273826126,
      0.7220026350461133,
      0.6173872617387262,
      0.8063241106719368
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_59",
    "order": 11
